Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに なぜ斬り伏せられぬ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗れた理由は―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.10,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,If you want to know why you lost,
