Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.18,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,have Liao tell you in the next world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:21.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけー！
