Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:45.88,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,But... Don't die, Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:45.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 死ぬな 王騎よ！
